        "Green Grocer (10185) followed in 2008 - perhaps the best-loved modular to this day: the sand-green townhouse with its delicatessen, bay window and interior staircase. Together with Market Street (10190), this early trio forms the holy grail of the series - and the sets are correspondingly rare and expensive today.",
